---
---

<section id="contact" class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 md:px-16 py-36 md:py-44 overflow-hidden">

  <!-- Giant watermark text -->
  <span
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2
           font-serif font-black text-[260px] md:text-[340px] leading-none
           text-gold/[0.025] whitespace-nowrap tracking-tighter pointer-events-none select-none"
  >
    NEXT 1
  </span>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <span class="section-label text-center block mb-5 reveal">// Sẵn sàng chưa?</span>

    <h2
      class="font-serif font-black text-[clamp(40px,7vw,90px)] leading-[1] tracking-[-0.03em] mb-8 reveal"
      style="animation-delay: 0.1s"
    >
      Xây dựng tài sản<br />
      <span class="italic font-normal text-gold">không phải cảm xúc.</span>
    </h2>

    <p
      class="text-[17px] md:text-lg text-white/75 max-w-[480px] mx-auto mb-14 leading-relaxed font-light reveal"
      style="animation-delay: 0.2s"
    >
      Một cộng đồng mạnh không phải vì giỏi nhất — mà vì kỷ luật nhất. Bước tiếp theo là của bạn.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">
      <a
        href="#membership"
        class="px-10 py-4 bg-gold text-ink text-[13px] font-semibold tracking-[0.12em] uppercase
               no-underline transition-all duration-250
               hover:bg-gold-light hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(201,168,76,0.35)]"
      >
        Tham gia NEXT 1 ngay
      </a>
      <a
        href="mailto:next1community@gmail.com"
        class="px-10 py-4 border border-white/40 text-white/80 text-[13px] font-normal tracking-[0.12em] uppercase
               no-underline transition-all duration-250 hover:border-gold hover:text-gold"
      >
        Liên hệ chúng tôi
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
